Package ticket

Class AbstractTicket

java.lang.Object
ticket.AbstractTicket
All Implemented Interfaces:
ITicket
Direct Known Subclasses:
BusTicket, BusTicketSingleton, PlaneTicket, PlaneTicketSingleton, TrainTicket, TrainTicketSingleton
public abstract class AbstractTicket
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITicket
Abstract class representing methods shared across all ticket types. The following methods are required by default when generating tickets for users. Passenger Name Route ID Departure Date and Time Arrival Date and Time Departure Location Arrival Location Class of Service This abstraction uses the same Calendar util from the interface.
Since:
10-07-2019
